n, k = [int(s) for s in input().split()]
    a = [int(s) for s in input().split()]
    graph = [[] for i in range(n)]
    for i in range(n-1):
        u, v = [int(s) for s in input().split()]
        graph[u-1].append(v-1)
        graph[v-1].append(u-1)
    def dfs(node, visited):
        visited[node] = True
        for i in graph[node]:
            if not visited[i]:
                dfs(i, visited)
    def preorder(node, visited):
        visited[node] = True
        for i in graph[node]:
            if not visited[i]:
                preorder(i, visited)
                a[node] = min(a[node], a[i])
    visited = [False] * n
    dfs(0, visited)
    visited = [False] * n
    preorder(0, visited)
    print(a[0])

N, T = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    cash = []
    time = []
    for i in range(N):
        c, t = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
        cash.append(c)
        time.append(t)
    cash.sort(reverse=True)
    time.sort()
    total = 0
    for i in range(N):
        if time[i] < T:
            total += cash[i]
            T -= time[i]
        else:
            break
    print(total)
